data.description: ABSOLUTELY DARLING 2/2 COLONY Patio VILLA.  Pretty as a picture from first glance, this freshly painted home is perfect for year-round enjoyment, seasonal use or investment.  You MUST come and see this immaculately maintained home to truly appreciate it's charm. It is Centrally located in the Village of ST. CHARLES with easy access to all The Villages has to offer. This popular model has an OPEN Concept with an Eat-in Kitchen, Large Breakfast Bar, Closet Pantry and opens to the Spacious Living and Dining rooms with VAULTED CEILINGS. The Kitchen has CHERRY Cabinets, a New Sink, Fridge and Microwave.  You’ll really appreciate the Pantry Closet and PULL-OUT Shelving. The Master Suite has a SPACIOUS WALK-IN CLOSET and a Newly designed Master Bath with a Walk-in Shower. The Guest Room is perfect for the occasional guest with it's BUILT IN MURPHY BED and the Guest Bath has a Tub/Shower combo. The NEW, GLASS ENCLOSED LANAI with Epoxy Painted Floor has Heat & Air.  The Lanai faces SOUTHEAST – A perfect spot that can be enjoyed all day long! The home has a NEWER HVAC (2021), NEW LAMINATE FLOORING THROUGHOUT, the Washer & Dryer are newer, and there is a NEW ROOF credit of $8,500.00 at the closing!! The 1½ car garage has plenty of room for 1 car and 1 golf cart.  This is a great home!  Fabulously priced, meticulously maintained VILLA.... A MUST SEE!
